					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It looks like you are thinking of the branch instructions as &quot;if &lt;condition&gt;	goto label&quot;, which is okay, but it can sometimes work out better for code structure to invert the test and branch over the code that you want to execute.<br /><br />As a simple example if you wanted to do something if A &gt;30h<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">cmp #$30<br />beq skip<br />bcc skip<br />; do stuff here when A is greater than $30<br />skip:<br /></div></div>

					
							<br /><br />
							<span class="gensmall">Last edited by <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4680">Movax12</a> on Sun Aug 24, 2014 4:47 pm, edited 1 time in total.</span>
						<br clear="all" /><br />

